        </span> <!----></a></div></div></div><div class="h-[50px] lg:h-[90px]"></div><div class="h-[1px] bg-lavender mx-[16px] md:mx-[52px]"></div><div class="h-[50px] lg:h-[90px]"></div><div class="flair-container text-center md:text-left"><div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 lg:grid-cols-2"><div class="min-h-[320px] h-[320px] overflow-hidden rounded-[5px] inner-img:h-full inner-img:object-contain inner-img:mx-auto md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 md:min-h-[264px] md:max-h-[264px] md:rounded-[10px] lg:min-h-[456px] lg:max-h-[456px] md:order-2"><picture><source media="(min-width: 1280px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/668x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/1336x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 2x"><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/588x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/1176x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 2x"><source media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/460x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/920x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 2x"><source media="(min-width: 640px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/736x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/1472x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1560x1290/a36976b6bb/limitless-salesforce-automations.png 2x"><source media="(min-width: 480px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyb