        Payroll for Manufacturing
      </a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li class="w-full sm:last-of-type:hidden"><p class="font-700 text-charcoal inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">Information</p> <div class="bg-lavender h-[1px] w-full sm:hidden"></div> <div class="h-[16px] sm:h-[24px]"></div> <ul class="space-y-[8px]"><li class="mr-[16px]"><div false="isSubItemsExtended = !isSubItemsExtended" class="flex items-center space-x-[3px] cursor-pointer max-w-max"><a href="/en/blog/" class="font-400 text-light-gray inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">
      Blog
